---
layout: "default"
title: "eGift"
---

<header class="header-promo">
    <div class="container header-promo--inner">
        <img src="<%= @getUrl("egift/egift.png") %>" alt="">
        <section class="header-promo--box">
            <h1>Boss Revolution<sup>SM</sup> eGift</h1>
            <h4>Shopping without stress? Send an e-Gift</h4>
            <p>Send a virtual gift card from our wide range of popular merchants. The card will be delivered electronically to anyone you select – along with a personalized message from you.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</header>

<div class="container">

    <article class="island island-default">
        
        <section class="dyad dyad-gap-small dyad-sm-vertical dyad-1-2 dyad--1_5-2 dyad-reverse">
            <div class="dyad--first dyad--stretch text-center">
                <div class="island island-condenced island-alt island-no-margin">
                    <img src="<%= @getUrl("egift/egift-flyer.png") %>" alt="BossRevolution eGift merchants">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dyad--second">
                <div class="spec-margin-top spec-margin-left">
                    <h1 class="offset-v-bottom">No Gift Wrap Necessary</h1>
                    <ul class="svg-list svg-list--sm">
                        <li class="svg-list--item"><h3>Popular merchants</h3></li>
                        <li class="svg-list--item"><h3>Instant Electronic Delivery</h3></li>
                        <li class="svg-list--item"><h3>No Fees</h3></li>
                        <li class="svg-list--item"><h3>Use card in-store, online or over phone*</h3></li>
                    </ul>
                    <h2 class="brand-color bordered-top offset-v-top" style="width: 93%;">Order Today at Your Participating Boss Revolution Retailer</h2>
                    <h3 class="h3-thin offset-v-top-sm no-offset-v-bottom">Choose the gift and the amount, <br />we send it electronically</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </article>

    <article class="island island-default">

        <h2 class="island--title">How It Works</h2>

        <section class="how-works how-works-4-blocks how-works-number-centered">
            <div class="how-works--block">
                <p>
                    <img src="<%= @getUrl("egift/how-it-works-egift-01.png") %>" alt="step 1">
                </p>
                <h3>Select the e-gift card that you want to send</h3>
                <p>Choose from many popular merchants.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-works--block">
                <p>
                    <img src="<%= @getUrl("egift/how-it-works-egift-02.png") %>" alt="step 2">
                </p>
                <h3>Provide recipient information to the Boss Revolution retailer</h3>
                <p>Choose SMS or email delivery.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-works--block">
                <p>
                    <img src="<%= @getUrl("egift/how-it-works-egift-03.png") %>" alt="step 3">
                </p>
                <h3>Specify the amount of&nbsp;the&nbsp;gift&nbsp;card to&nbsp;send</h3>
                <p>From $25 - $100.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-works--block">
                <p>
                    <img class="offset-v-top-sm" src="<%= @getUrl("egift/how-it-works-egift-04.png") %>" alt="step 4">
                </p>
                <h3>We’ll deliver the electronic gift card instantly</h3>
                <p>Card details will be sent securely to&nbsp;the&nbsp;recipient.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

    </article>

    <article class="island island-default ">

        <h2 class="island--title"><span>For terms and conditions of each merchant, <br />click on its logo below</span></h2>

        <section class="island island-transparent text-center">
